Package: estatusbar
Type: Package
Title: Register Task Progress, Display Statusbar, Estimate Time of Completion
Version: 0.5.0
Author: Petar Mimica
Maintainer: Petar Mimica <petar.mimica@gmail.com>
Description: This is an R port of a Fortran module that was used 
 in the astrophysical codes SPEV and MRGENESIS. The user can register the task completion
 fraction as it progresses and display a progress/status bar. The package uses several 
 algorithms to estimate the time of completion.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    R6,
    lubridate
